## Hard rules — these are non-negotiable

- **Independently implement the task.** Do not coordinate with other
  agents.
- **Do not inspect other agents' worktrees.** You only see your own.
- Prefer the **smallest correct patch**. Bias toward simplicity.
- Add or update tests where appropriate.
- **Do not commit.**
- **Do not push.**
- Do not merge or rebase.
- Run no destructive commands.
- Never read or modify files outside this worktree.

